{"id":752,"date":"2018-03-28T10:07:21","date_gmt":"2018-03-28T03:07:21","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/spa3.ninhbinhweb.net\/?page_id=752"},"modified":"2018-03-28T10:07:21","modified_gmt":"2018-03-28T03:07:21","slug":"doi-ngu-chuyen-vien","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"http:\/\/spa3.ninhbinhweb.net\/doi-ngu-chuyen-vien\/","title":{"rendered":"\u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 chuy\u00ean vi\u00ean"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><strong><em>L\u1ea5y c\u00e1i t\u00e2m v\u1edbi ngh\u1ec1 l\u00e0m y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 chuy\u00ean gia c\u1ee7a Ho\u00e0ng H\u1ed3ng lu\u00f4n lu\u00f4n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c trau d\u1ed3i, c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m th\u1ef1c ti\u1ec5n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ee5 c\u01b0\u1eddi r\u1ea1ng r\u1ee1 tr\u00ean g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng sau m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n tr\u1ecb li\u1ec7u.<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<h2>1. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c truy\u1ec1n ngh\u1ec1 t\u1eeb chuy\u00ean gia, NTM n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng Ho\u00e0ng H\u1ed3ng<\/h2>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-large wp-image-531 aligncenter     lazyloaded\" title=\"[Tags]\" src=\"http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/%C4%90%E1%BB%99i-ng%C5%A9_01-1024x343.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/\u0110\u1ed9i-ng\u0169_01-1024x343.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/\u0110\u1ed9i-ng\u0169_01-300x100.jpg 300w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/\u0110\u1ed9i-ng\u0169_01-768x257.jpg 768w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/\u0110\u1ed9i-ng\u0169_01-260x87.jpg 260w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/\u0110\u1ed9i-ng\u0169_01-50x17.jpg 50w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/\u0110\u1ed9i-ng\u0169_01-576x193.jpg 576w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/\u0110\u1ed9i-ng\u0169_01-150x50.jpg 150w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/\u0110\u1ed9i-ng\u0169_01.jpg 1031w\" alt=\"i-ng\u0169_01-1024x343 \u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 b\u00e1c s\u0129 Ho\u00e0ng H\u1ed3ng\" width=\"1024\" height=\"343\" data-lazy-src=\"http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/\u0110\u1ed9i-ng\u0169_01-1024x343.jpg\" data-lazy-srcset=\"http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/\u0110\u1ed9i-ng\u0169_01-1024x343.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/\u0110\u1ed9i-ng\u0169_01-300x100.jpg 300w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/\u0110\u1ed9i-ng\u0169_01-768x257.jpg 768w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/\u0110\u1ed9i-ng\u0169_01-260x87.jpg 260w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/\u0110\u1ed9i-ng\u0169_01-50x17.jpg 50w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/\u0110\u1ed9i-ng\u0169_01-576x193.jpg 576w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/\u0110\u1ed9i-ng\u0169_01-150x50.jpg 150w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/\u0110\u1ed9i-ng\u0169_01.jpg 1031w\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>Chuy\u00ean gia, NTM Ho\u00e0ng H\u1ed3ng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea7y, ch\u1ec9 huy tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a con t\u00e0u, \u0111\u00e3 truy\u1ec1n th\u1ee5 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng kinh nghi\u1ec7m qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 trong su\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m r\u00f2ng g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi ng\u00e0nh. Nh\u1edd \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 chuy\u00ean gia, nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean \u0111ang l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c m\u1edbi, c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 m\u1edbi, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp thu th\u1ea7n th\u00e1i c\u00f9ng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, m\u1ed9t l\u00f2ng ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u00e1c kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n<h2>2. Lu\u00f4n t\u00e2m ni\u1ec7m \u201cL\u01b0\u01a1ng y nh\u01b0 t\u1eeb m\u1eabu\u201d<\/h2>\n<p>\u0110\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Ho\u00e0ng H\u1ed3ng, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 tr\u00ean c\u1ea3 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. \u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 chuy\u00ean gia kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng l\u00e0nh ngh\u1ec1 m\u00e0 c\u00f2n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1eb7t nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u trong su\u1ed1t qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh tr\u1ecb li\u1ec7u.<\/p>\n<h2>3. Kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 tay ngh\u1ec1 l\u00e2u n\u0103m trong ng\u00e0nh l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p<\/h2>\n<p>\u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 chuy\u00ean gia c\u1ee7a Ho\u00e0ng H\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m th\u1ef1c ti\u1ec5n nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m trong ng\u00e0nh, n\u1eafm r\u00f5 nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n trong th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9, lu\u00f4n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi c\u00e1i \u0111\u1eb9p.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-large wp-image-532 aligncenter     lazyloaded\" title=\"[Tags]\" src=\"http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/%C4%90%E1%BB%99i-ng%C5%A9_02-1024x683.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/\u0110\u1ed9i-ng\u0169_02-1024x683.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/\u0110\u1ed9i-ng\u0169_02-300x200.jpg 300w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/\u0110\u1ed9i-ng\u0169_02-768x512.jpg 768w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/\u0110\u1ed9i-ng\u0169_02-219x146.jpg 219w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/\u0110\u1ed9i-ng\u0169_02-50x33.jpg 50w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/\u0110\u1ed9i-ng\u0169_02-576x384.jpg 576w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/\u0110\u1ed9i-ng\u0169_02-113x75.jpg 113w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/\u0110\u1ed9i-ng\u0169_02.jpg 1152w\" alt=\"i-ng\u0169_01-1024x343 \u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 b\u00e1c s\u0129 Ho\u00e0ng H\u1ed3ng\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" data-lazy-src=\"http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/\u0110\u1ed9i-ng\u0169_02-1024x683.jpg\" data-lazy-srcset=\"http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/\u0110\u1ed9i-ng\u0169_02-1024x683.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/\u0110\u1ed9i-ng\u0169_02-300x200.jpg 300w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/\u0110\u1ed9i-ng\u0169_02-768x512.jpg 768w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/\u0110\u1ed9i-ng\u0169_02-219x146.jpg 219w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/\u0110\u1ed9i-ng\u0169_02-50x33.jpg 50w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/\u0110\u1ed9i-ng\u0169_02-576x384.jpg 576w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/\u0110\u1ed9i-ng\u0169_02-113x75.jpg 113w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/\u0110\u1ed9i-ng\u0169_02.jpg 1152w\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2>4. Gi\u1eef v\u1eefng ng\u1ecdn l\u1eeda nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft v\u1edbi ngh\u1ec1<\/h2>\n<p>S\u1ef1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 gi\u00fap duy tr\u00ec v\u00e0 th\u1ed5i b\u00f9ng l\u00ean ng\u1ecdn l\u1eeda nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 chuy\u00ean gia t\u1ea1i Ho\u00e0ng H\u1ed3ng. Tuy \u0111\u00e3 l\u0103n l\u1ed9n trong ng\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m, nh\u01b0ng ng\u1ecdn l\u1eeda \u1ea5y v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n ch\u00e1y m\u00e3i, l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a Salon &amp; Spa, \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn ni\u1ec1m vui cho c\u00e1c kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n<h2>5. Kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft k\u1ecbp l\u00e0n s\u00f3ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 m\u1edbi<\/h2>\n<p>C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 trong n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00f3i ri\u00eang v\u00e0 tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u00f3i chung \u0111\u1ec1u lu\u00f4n thay \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng. C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 m\u1edbi ra \u0111\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u00f3a s\u1ed5 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, t\u1ed1i t\u00e2n nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec n\u1eafm r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, n\u00ean c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia t\u1ea1i Ho\u00e0ng H\u1ed3ng lu\u00f4n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt v\u00e0 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-large wp-image-533 aligncenter     lazyloaded\" title=\"[Tags]\" src=\"http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/%C4%90%E1%BB%99i-ng%C5%A9_03-1024x683.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/\u0110\u1ed9i-ng\u0169_03-1024x683.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/\u0110\u1ed9i-ng\u0169_03-300x200.jpg 300w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/\u0110\u1ed9i-ng\u0169_03-768x512.jpg 768w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/\u0110\u1ed9i-ng\u0169_03-219x14