ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd mang \u0111\u1ebfn cho b\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t di\u1ec7n m\u1ea1o ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n m\u1edbi, khi\u1ebfn b\u1ea1n lu\u00f4n r\u1ea1ng ng\u1eddi m\u1ed7i s\u1edbm mai.<\/p>\n<p><strong>HO\u00c0NG H\u1ed2NG SALON &amp; SPA<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>S\u1ed1 7, Ng\u00f5 62, \u0110inh Ti\u00ean Ho\u00e0ng, TP Ninh B\u00ecnh<\/p>\n<p>Tel: 0303893196<\/p>\n<p>Mobile: 0916.622.622<\/p>\n<p>T\u01b0 v\u1ea5n &amp; CSKH (24\/7): 0303 893.196<\/p>\n<p>Th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c 8:00 \u2013 21:00 L\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3 ng\u00e0y l\u1ec5 v\u00e0 Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>L\u1ea5y c\u00e1i t\u00e2m v\u1edbi ngh\u1ec1 l\u00e0m y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 chuy\u00ean gia c\u1ee7a Ho\u00e0ng H\u1ed3ng lu\u00f4n lu\u00f4n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c trau d\u1ed3i, c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m th\u1ef1c ti\u1ec5n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ee5 c\u01b0\u1eddi r\u1ea1ng r\u1ee1 tr\u00ean g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng sau m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n tr\u1ecb li\u1ec7u. 1. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c truy\u1ec1n ngh\u1ec1 t\u1eeb [&hellip;]\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"page-right-sidebar.php","meta":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/spa3.ninhbinhweb.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/752"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/spa3.ninhbinhweb.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/spa3.ninhbinhweb.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/spa3.ninhbinhweb.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/spa3.ninhbinhweb.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=752"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/spa3.ninhbinhweb.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/752\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/spa3.ninhbinhweb.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/